   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="header">
            <p>Verwandtschajtsweisung für Eisbeth, Gattin des Hans Pyber</p>
         </div>                   <div type="entry" resp="rs">
            <p> Einbr. 3 Zg. (Indez: Item frewntschaft Elspeten Hansen des Pibers uxor) <rs
                  type="event" ref="#ev__StB_I_199">Item des nachsten eritags vor sand Mertten tag
                  kom auch fur den rat <rs type="fn" role="witness"><rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__elisabeth_StB_I_199"><roleName type="title">fraw</roleName> Elspet,
                           <roleName type="kin" corresp="#pe__johann_piber_StB_I_199"
                              ><add>hawsfraw</add></roleName><rs type="person"
                           ref="#pe__johann_piber_StB_I_199">Hannsen hawsfraw des Pybers</rs></rs>,
                     und hat da beweist mit den erbern leuten, als si ze recht solt, mit <rs
                        type="person" ref="#pe__gilg_druml_StB_I_199"><roleName type="title"
                              ><add>erbern</add></roleName>Giligen dem Drumlein</rs>, <rs
                        type="person" ref="#pe__leutold_maurer_StB_I_199"><roleName type="title"
                              ><add>erbern</add></roleName>Leutlein dem <roleName type="prof"
                           cert="unknown">Mawrer</roleName></rs> und mit <rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__jakob_chaeufel_StB_I_199"><roleName type="title"
                           ><add>erbern</add></roleName>Jacoben dem <roleName type="prof"
                           cert="unknown">Cheufflein</roleName></rs></rs>, das <rs type="fn"
                     role="recipient"><rs type="person" ref="#pe__elisabeth_StB_I_199">si <roleName
                           type="kin" corresp="#pe__anna_StB_I_199"><add>recht
                           swestern</add></roleName><roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__margarethe_StB_I_199"><add>recht
                        swestern</add></roleName></rs> und <rs type="person"
                        ref="#pe__anna_StB_I_199">Ann, <roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__niklas_guster_StB_I_199"><add>hawsfraw</add></roleName>
                        <rs type="person" ref="#pe__niklas_guster_StB_I_199">Niclas hawsfraw des
                              <roleName type="prof" cert="unknown">Gusters</roleName></rs><roleName
                           type="kin" corresp="#pe__elisabeth_StB_I_199"><add>recht
                           swestern</add></roleName><roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__margarethe_StB_I_199"><add>recht
                        swestern</add></roleName></rs></rs>, und <rs type="fn" role="issuer"><rs
                        type="person" ref="#pe__margarethe_StB_I_199"><roleName type="title"
                           >fraw</roleName> Margret, weilnt <roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__jakob_phister_QGW_II_I_799"><add>hawsfraw</add></roleName>
                        <rs type="person" ref="#pe__jakob_phister_QGW_II_I_799">Jacobs hawsfraw des
                              <roleName type="prof" cert="unknown">Phisters</roleName></rs>, der got
                           <roleName type="dead">gnad</roleName>, drey <roleName type="kin"
                           corresp="#pe__elisabeth_StB_I_199">recht swestern</roleName><roleName
                           type="kin" corresp="#pe__anna_StB_I_199"><add>recht
                           swestern</add></roleName></rs> gewesen sind von vater und von
                  mueter</rs>. Als darumb die obgenanten erbern leut mit irn trewn an ayde stat vor
                  offem rat habent gesagt, als si ze recht solten.</rs>
            </p>
         </div>
